Our lab are always recruiting **M.Phil. or Ph.D** students with strong academic background and/or solid programming skill. Before you apply, please first read the [**Application Guideline**](/guidelines/guideline_eng.pdf). For Chinese students, please refer to [**SIGMA Lab申请指南**](/guidelines/guideline_chinese.pdf).

Currently, we have no position for postdoc researchers and research assistants for our lab.
